description:
This is a 28 minute workout called 'Full-body mat workout for period and PMS | Low impact + no repeat' from the channel CBC Life.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: POV: You want to workout, but it’s your time of the month...

In this video, fitness coach Beverley Cheng will lead you through a 25-minute low-impact circuit workout that encourages you to move light, move slow — and move with intention. No major cardio exercises or jumping here. You’ll start with a relaxing warm-up, then shift into some energizing bodyweight exercises that don’t repeat, in order to keep things interesting.
